/**
 * /spaces — 301 Redirect (space entity type merged into model)
 *
 * The `space` entity type (HuggingFace interactive demos) was consolidated into
 * `model`: a space demos a model, so the demo signal belongs on that model. The
 * spaces catalog 301-redirects to /models — a permanent, SEO-honest move (not a
 * soft-404). Reversible: restore the prior UniversalCatalog SSR page from git.
 */
return Astro.redirect('/models', 301);
